{"tid":2169460,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[流出] 葉劉淑儀  迷人粉色套裝","createTime":"2020-08-22T13:27:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-22T16:05:41.000Z","uid":301666,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b73e1988452a27931bf744e35ebd15d1d93a557a","tid":2169460,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:27:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/117942785_10157485433112157_2336540704811668336_o.jpg?_nc_cat=110&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=P4mLQQlVQ_UAX9iZyJ9&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=b02afa0637a2e8a705e84ee9f2ab6e61&amp;oe=5F67DDA5\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F117942785_10157485433112157_2336540704811668336_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D110%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_ohc%3DP4mLQQlVQ_UAX9iZyJ9%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26tp%3D14%26oh%3Db02afa0637a2e8a705e84ee9f2ab6e61%26oe%3D5F67DDA5&h=029bd0c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【再訪Sam's Tailor  支持本地經濟】<br />\n<br />\n日前再到 Sam's Tailor 拜訪第三代掌門人 Roshan Melwani。較早前我到該店並在Roshan建議下，訂做了一套仿照某大牌子款式的粉紅色套裝，想不到數天已起貨，裁剪亦非常貼身及舒適，我對其出品十分滿意。是次穿上新衣到訪， Roshan 笑說我可以做其「生招牌」並誠邀合照，其後他建議我再度身訂做新套裝，我也欣然接納。這次他建議用上法國材料，訂造一套不同款式的套裝。<br />\n<br />\n傾談間想不到 Roshan 竟然大吐苦水。他表示在香港長大，生活多年，環境從未試過像現時般艱苦。經過去年黑暴肆虐及疫情影響，尖沙咀一帶商店生意遭受嚴重打擊，市況甚至可以用「慘淡」來形容，他慨嘆由於商品要瘋狂減價，故此邊際利潤變得十分微薄，他相信現時香港各行各業也是生意難做，商戶只好望天打掛。<br />\n<br />\n幸好他生性樂觀，正努力為 Sam's Tailor 尋找新商機，更建議我向特區政府一眾女高官，推銷本地產品(包括他們生產的衣服)，並歡迎她們隨時到店度身訂做套裝。我笑說這是好提議，並一口答應他一試無妨，<br />\n<br />\n其實香港時下女士的服飾大多是現成服裝(ready to wear)，難得Sam's Tailor度身訂做的女裝手工不錯，價錢亦算相宜。如今本地零售市道疲弱，市民消費力大減，假如一眾特區政府女高官能夠帶頭示範，身體力行光顧本地產品，支持一流裁縫，相信定能促進本地經濟，為市道打下強心針。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157485433382157&amp;id=16720522156\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fstory.php%3Fstory_fbid%3D10157485433382157%26id%3D16720522156&d=aFiO92UEzPWfS5u3FViI6fTmwccdIWYcDO8ZGhePZ24%3D&h=dc09a66a\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/story.php?story_fbid=10157485433382157&amp;id=16720522156</a>"},{"pid":"5a90ea84d29d481412d3846a2696834a1d91d756","tid":2169460,"uid":301666,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-22T13:29:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/117931505_10157485433127157_1183468680708865840_o.jpg?_nc_cat=100&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=jt9rpCoHSNwAX_EV0ys&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=bcee9e084084eeff39db02122b5eb749&amp;oe=5F67960C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F117931505_10157485433127157_1183468680708865840_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D100%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_ohc%3Djt9rpCoHSNwAX_EV0ys%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26tp%3D14%26oh%3Dbcee9e084084eeff39db02122b5eb749%26oe%3D5F67960C&h=b933b429&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/118324771_10157485432877157_3561471483479250806_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=oA-rXCrkrGsAX9_vdky&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg4-1.xx&amp;tp=14&amp;oh=02d06086fdf6a102f13843b564a737ec&amp;oe=5F661D0C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F118324771_10157485432877157_3561471483479250806_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_sid%3D8024bb%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_ohc%3DoA-rXCrkrGsAX9_vdky%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg4-1.xx%26tp%3D14%26oh%3D02d06086fdf6a102f13843b564a737ec%26oe%3D5F661D0C&h=e88a3a31&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg4-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/117965202_10157485433192157_6716086210804595862_o.jpg?_nc_cat=109&amp;_nc_sid=8024bb&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=BaxR_d7sxwwAX9Ob2lk&amp;_nc